Uses of Package
edu.udel.cis.taschd.ca

  • Packages that use edu.udel.cis.taschd.ca 
    Package Description
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.assign
    The course module provides classes for representing assignments of course instances and course assistant for a specified term.
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.ca
    The course module provides classes for representing course assistants and the course assistant pool.
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.course
    The course module provides classes for representing courses, course instances, sections, and the course pool.
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.db
    The db module provides classes for storing and retrieving course and CA information.
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.extract
    The extract module provides classes and methods for extracting CA Schedule, Courses Schedule information from WebReg and maps to CourseInstance and CourseAssistant Classes
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.gen
    The course module provides classes for representing the generator of assignments of courses to course assistants.
    edu.udel.cis.taschd.userinterface
    The UI module provides the interface an user to perform all the operations in taschd.
